 193:src/engine.cpp ****         // New voice: snap the continuous DSP state to this voice's targets so the
 194:src/engine.cpp ****         // previous voice's settings don't bleed in (esp. the slow-closing cutoff
 195:src/engine.cpp ****         // and the ladder filter's stored energy). Voice changes only happen while
 196:src/engine.cpp ****         // silent (FSR gesture) or at a drum-tap onset, so snapping is clean and
 197:src/engine.cpp ****         // gives each MultiVoice hit a fresh start.
